@jsjason You addressed my comments.
@shravanmn Could you check if Jason addressed your comments? Can we also resolve the Scatter API?

This issue currently blocks [REEF-420](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/REEF-420).

Most of our Avro Serializers don't have instance variables and have default constructor only. Comparing static methods and using injection to use singleton, an advantage of using static is simple. While using injection/singleton would allow us to use interface for serializer. 

For this particular PR, as it is to replace original serializer which used static. I am Ok to merge this PR and leaving static/singleton discussion for future. 

@markusweimer , what do you think?
